name: Sam Toro
interests: Traveling, Cooking exotic cuisines, Hiking, Digital art
summary: Sam Toro is a 28-year-old, non-binary UI/UX Designer from Seattle, WA, now living in Los Angeles, CA. They're fluent in English, Spanish, and Chinese and highly value community, diversity, and creativity. They enjoy traveling, cooking exotic cuisines, hiking, and digital art. Sam is open minded as they hold agnostic religious beliefs and liberal political views. A graduate from the University of Southern California, Sam is interested in finding a life partner and prefers a monogamous relationship. They hope to have children in the future, and have a cat and fish as pets. As a Taurus and ENFJ personality type, Sam leads an active lifestyle and occasionally enjoys a drink. In a partner, they would like to interact with someone who shares their active lifestyle and has no exposure to drugs or smoking. They would prefer someone who never had children but is open to starting a family.
